      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "(Scripps News Association.)\n\n\nLOS ANGELES, Oct. 26. - The\nw. G. T. U. held an all day evan\ngelistic service at Trinity Methodist\nchurch, conducted by Miss Eliza w.\nGreenwood of New York. There\nwas a discussion of the advisable\nity of inserting prohibition In the\npledge. The conferences agreed\nmore can be done by persuasion\nthan rule."
